msgid "`return_mode` 参数控制返回的数据类型："
msgstr ""
"The `return_mode` parameter controls the data type of the returned data:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:391
msgid "提示：`return_mode` 仅在 `enable_event=False` 时生效；事件流模式始终返回原始响应对象或流式 chunk。"
msgstr ""
"Tip: `return_mode` only takes effect when `enable_event=False`; event stream"
